Euphin "I'm-not-small!" - Druid of 29 Wolfspirits <BR>
Euphoros "Destroyer-of-the-Worlds" - Wizard of 11 Blasts</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/umininiu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mininiu</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 81<br> <font color=#333333>(9/10/02 10:00:54 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=351.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: where..? </span><hr size=1> Take a partner and head to your favorite hunting spot. A druid will let you tank and also pratice his defense. But you have the heal so you can tank more.<br>
<br>
I personnally praticed defense and dodge in Mistmore. Some interesting stuffs there. Your faction with bard and dragons go higher. As a DE I find convenient to be able to sell in any bard guild (freeport for example). Cash not too bad at all, 5 plats per kills some times. And since luclin it should be near desert so you'll find old players with lots of experience out there soloing or pling. Maybe something to try. <p>Mininiu CrazyMagus
53 Magician 
